title: OUT NOW: Small Island Big Song Live on KEXP

description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Small Island Big Song performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded February 21, 2024.

Songs:
Pinagsanga
Sarbon
Aoka
Kinimale
Phawhaw
Gasikara
Mauruuru Te Atua
Pacific Log Drumming
Dodo

Performers:
Emlyn (Mauritius) - Lead Vocals, Calabash, Maravanne

Sammy (aka Tarika Sammy) (Madagascar) - Lead Vocals, Valiha, Jejy, Kabosy, Sodina, Percussion

Aremiti (Tahiti/French Polynesia) - Lead Vocals, Ukulele, Pacific Percussion, Nose Flute
